{"tid":2065001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大懵侍應酒精噴壺當「探熱槍」 男童遭噴眼急送院","createTime":"2020-06-15T08:27:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T08:32:28.000Z","uid":4646,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f1b35db28a30353d6a9e4fcd690ecfc5630b8a60","tid":2065001,"uid":4646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T08:27:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.ohpama.com/wp-content/uploads/master/2020/06/2020061514234442312.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohpama.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fmaster%2F2020%2F06%2F2020061514234442312.jpg&h=ad54b6cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n^巴打絲打 Facebook Club FB<br />\n<br />\n疫情下到餐廳食飯，都要先量體溫才可進入，不過有「大懵」侍應就錯將裝有75&deg;酒精的噴壺當成探熱槍，噴向一名男童雙眼，令男童張不開眼，最後更要到醫院洗眼。<br />\n<br />\n有網民在Facebook群組發貼，「有位好醒目嘅侍應，攞咗支酒精噴壺當體溫槍，然後幫個小朋友量度體溫」。有網民指，從相片看事發地點應是葵芳新都會商場。只見男童痛苦地緊閉雙眼，眼睛一直未能睜開，最後更需要到醫院處理。發帖網民提醒所有家長「之後注意類似由第三者產生的失魂意外」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.ohpama.com/wp-content/uploads/master/2020/06/2020061514234468616.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohpama.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fmaster%2F2020%2F06%2F2020061514234468616.jpg&h=c1a3b568&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不少網民都很擔心小朋友的情況，指如果酒精入眼應立刻用水清洗。有人批評侍應犯的錯不合常理，但亦有人認為是無心之失，「又唔怪得個待應，佢不是醫護人員」、「我唔會話佢啱，但佢一日接觸幾百個人，換一換手都有可能噴錯」，更有人見過更嚴重的失誤，「我見過有個阿姐用漂白水噴個阿叔眼」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.ohpama.com/wp-content/uploads/master/2020/06/2020061514234593911.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohpama.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fmaster%2F2020%2F06%2F2020061514234593911.jpg&h=b64e264c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c24192eaf7854bf18d3bc5e23f3668571e524e04","tid":2065001,"uid":4646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T08:28:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ohpama.com/560363/生活熱話/生活熱話/大懵侍應酒精噴壺當「探熱槍」-男童遭噴眼急送院/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohpama.com%2F560363%2F%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1%2F%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1%2F%E5%A4%A7%E6%87%B5%E4%BE%8D%E6%87%89%E9%85%92%E7%B2%BE%E5%99%B4%E5%A3%BA%E7%95%B6%E3%80%8C%E6%8E%A2%E7%86%B1%E6%A7%8D%E3%80%8D-%E7%94%B7%E7%AB%A5%E9%81%AD%E5%99%B4%E7%9C%BC%E6%80%A5%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2%2F&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7q3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=e5ba2188\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ohpama.com/560363/生活熱話/生活熱話/大懵侍應酒精噴壺當「探熱槍」-男童遭噴眼急送院/</a>"},{"pid":"a8a8e8f2d4be854d73bc6549ee81cc42741cf676","tid":2065001,"uid":227275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T08:30:43.000Z","msg":"有病睇醫生"},{"pid":"80a7f4b56be253a1a4f17d06c8a4d2aa0b9e4d72","tid":2065001,"uid":18012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T08:32:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw 細路好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8e3ab7ceefca550e38a360edf8b0b3db61e23b0","tid":2065001,"uid":235324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T08:32:28.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個細路慘到"}]}